title: Home, Family, Love - Rentals in Delray Beach. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Reference #:RX-10811641', 'Move in ready...', 'Turnkey 2/2 fully furnished, beautifully and professionally decorated/designed.', 'Perfect vacation unit.', 'Newly remodeled pool area and Tiki hut directly on the intracoastal.', 'Some boat slips are available for lease through other owners.', "This unit has everything you'll need for a fantastic stay (just bring toothbrush and swim trunks).", 'Includes: impact windows/doors, W&D in unit, stainless appliances, elevator access, etc.', 'Available for seasonal rental at $7,500 per month, also available as an annual rental and as an off-season rental.', "Quick drive to downtown Delray Beach, Atlantic Ave, Trader Joe's, Whole Foods, etc.", 'Private beach across the street and the owners will provide an umbrella and two chairs to enhance your stay.', 'Call to discuss...season will be here soon!', "Looking to buy, rent or sell please call me today🏠 Florida's Best Realty service🌎 <URL>", 'show contact info', '-Available 24/7']
